reviewText:
Be advised, this guy is selling these used. Dvd's are very scratched, cover is partly torn, clearly used.

With that said, the dvd itself is okay, but understand that it is 110% "solo" girls. No girl n guy, no girl n girl. Just girl. Occasionally girl n toy. If you are a fan of the entire theme of this dvd then you will still enjoy it. Just don't expect any hardcore fast jiggling, bouncing, flopping, etc. It's all kinda lazy motions, because it's solo.
